Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous out here, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You must live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving various harsh training,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,two outstanding young men
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,became the Scarlet Guardians that protect\Nthis very planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them Private Yuito Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The other one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is Private Nagi Karman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right before the memorable graduation ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the two promising young will display\Ntheir true potential to the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you want a real fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Will you surrender now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I found an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,ALARM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,THE GRADUATION CEREMONY IS ABOUT TO BEGIN\NPLEASE BE HURRY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,DANGER ZONE, NO ENTRY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Nagi Karman who will\Njoin the Scarlet Guardians today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"THE MUCH ANTICIPATED 567TH CLASS"\NToday is the day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"THE MUCH ANTICIPATED 567TH CLASS"\Nwhere the graduation ceremony of OSF begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All who made it into the OSF are elites that\Nwent through the harsh affinity tests of SAS.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's introduce the star recruit of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where my name comes in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"FROM A GLORIOUS BACKGROUND, OSF AS HIS GOAL"\NYuito Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the song of Chairman Jo Sumeragi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-of the New Himuka Government.\N-So it really was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"CHAIRMAN JO SUMERAGI OF NEW HIMUKA COUNCIL"\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"CHAIRMAN JO SUMERAGI OF NEW HIMUKA COUNCIL"\NHis ancestor was the founding father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the prestigious family's hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"KAITO SUMERAGI,  MINISTER OF OSF"\NHis brother, Kaito Sumeragi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Minister of New Himuka's OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave up his political career\Nto serve at the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There has been a concerning report lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,According to insider's information,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito's affinity for power is much lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can the prestigious and delicate young man
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,survive the harsh battle against the Others?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-This leaves a sour taste in my mouth.\N-Next news thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, just ignore those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact the my power is subpar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you are part of the OSF from starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We both gave it our best to make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been your dream to join the OSF\Nsince you were a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better keep this in mind, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,ALERT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,OTHERS ALERT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They just ruined our special day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Others alert has been issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The probabilities of attacks for\Ndifferent areas are as follow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who crushed the Other in one hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,receiver of First Class of Septentrions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"MAJOR KAREN TRAVERS, POWER: BRAIN EATER"\Nbrain eater, Karen Travers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Major Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"MAJOR FUBUKI SPRING, POWER: CRYOKINESIS"\NHe froze the Other with his cryokinesis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Fubuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to fight the way they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You must live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♪A crime in reality♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♪For Heaven's sake♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Accepts any fake♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♪And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Won't take it at all, I get sick♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪A girl looking back♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Casts the miracle into this instant world♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Did you lie♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Did you lie♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Spit the venom♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I know why♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've found a game of ecstasy♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Red Criminal gets life♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've never been in love♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Don't know when I started getting sick of this world♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪We will fly♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Someday I won't be crying♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've been sacrificing myself not to hurt anybody♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky for us, we made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We must be waiting for Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a cute girl in our class!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi Randall. Lovely Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the little girl next to her is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They are of the same age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She is looking at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not show your weakness so easily,\Nthey won't stop pestering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, you are always\Ntreating me like a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I was looking\Nat the guy next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A speech from Minister Kaito Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Only those with a noble ambition
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,will be chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I applaud your courage and passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In the country that is plagued by\Nattacks from the Others,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,those from the scout class that has\Noutstanding power,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the volunteer class that must\Ntrain to improve their power
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"POWER"\Nmust work as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Without your combined powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you will not overcome the challenges\Nahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We only know the enemies\Ncome from the Extinction Belt in stratosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still a number of mysteries to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why those with the powers\Nto stand against the monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,are our first line of defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,While you're carrying out your missions,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,do not forget the ambition you hold\Nin your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:09:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all 2168 of the students here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,will officially become part of New Himuka's OSF,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the Scarlet Guardians!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,NAGI KARMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,YUITO SUMERAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I could talk to Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How old were you when you were rescued?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The women in OSF from back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi Randall?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what you've been looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The eldest daughter of\Nthe noble Randall family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The person next to her\Nwas her younger sister, Kasane Randall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane's parents were killed\Nby Others when she was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Randalls took her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She became Naomi's sister,\Nwho was at the same age as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She was recruited into OSF\Nwhen she was 12 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She was at the top of\Nthe leaderboard in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi was in fifth place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They are totally elites!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane Randall...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Randall family...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,On my father's inauguration ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't find anything about\Nthe person who saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yuito,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,there is something I must know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she looks a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will woo Naomi instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Kasane is still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned this morning\Nyou had a dream about RED Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let go of the RED Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a dream was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it related to your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I am more worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if we would be in the same platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You are sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So I must protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, that was mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't know who saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even my brother knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We are on the same team!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi, it's been too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She is my childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He is Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't see you in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was in the scouted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Seto Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"CAPTAIN SETO NARUKAMI"\NI am Seto Narukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"POWER: ELECTROKINESIS"\NI am your captain starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As you all know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,starting today,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we will use the Struggle Arms System, SAS,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to share our powers in the battles\Nagainst our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,New members, please introduce yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, my power is electrokinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"2ND LIEUTENANT HANABI ICHIJO"\NI am Hanabi Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"POWER: PYROKINESIS"\NMy power is pyrokinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"PRIVATE NAGI KARMAN"\NI am Nagi Karman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"POWER: AEROKINESIS"\NMy power is aerokinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been my dream to join OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"PRIVATE YUITO SUMERAGI"\NI am Yuito Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"POWER PSYCHOKINESIS"\NMy power is psychokinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was rescued by the OSF as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do whatever I can to repay the kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The current members should\Nintroduce themselves too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"MAJOR TSUGUMI NAZAR"\NI am Tsugumi Nazar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"POWER: CLAIRVOYANCE"\NMy power is clairvoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my power...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to show how your clairvoyance work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be the famous Yuito Sumeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all over the news this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was talking about\Nthe Young Master Sumeragi's recruitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"CORPORAL KAGERO DONNE"\NFreshmen of the 567th class,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"POWER: INVISIBILITY"\NI am Kagero Donne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am what they called a latent genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A self-proclaimed genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain is always so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Others occurrences have been spotted
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,above Suzaku area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto Platoon and Kyoka Platoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,proceed to the area immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Alert level elevated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Combatants, please proceed\Nto the area immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm and go to the bunkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Anti-Others warfare has\Neliminated 85% of the Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of them are still falling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't introduced myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"2ND LIEUTENANT WATARU FRAZER"\NI am Wataru Frazer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"POWER: TELEPATHY"\NMy power is telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can connect to other people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will provide support from the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto Platoon, go to point E.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka Platoon, go to point F
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to eliminate the Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Seto Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Target confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well! Let's show them\Nwhat the Scarlet Guardians are made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You two stand by in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for reinforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to die on your first day at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this as a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. We are only volunteer soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We took down two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka Platoon arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed to the battles now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the support just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ALERT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, get us some reinforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Don't look so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to wait for reinforcement!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they didn't make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We will go to her rescue now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, you're great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, another wave is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I made up my mind long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become a soldier of OSF
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and become like the person who saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nagi!\N-Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-That hurts...\N-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, the Others are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,2ND LIEUTENANT NAOMI RANDALL\NPOWER: CLAIRVOYANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"2ND LIEUTENANT KASANE RANDALL"\NPOWER: TELEKINESIS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to die on your first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You must live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you are all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of Private Yuito Sumeragi's outstanding\Nperformance on his first day,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Other was successfully eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Private Sumeragi acquired an undeniable victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"CAPTAIN ARASHI SPRING, POWER: HYPERVELOCITY"\NThat's all for the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Captain Arashi Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I gave it my best just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"LIEUTENANT COLONEL LUKA TRAVERS"\NGetting the media's attention on your first day,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"POWER: TELEPORTATION"\Nthat must be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Colonel Luka Travers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sixth Class of Septentrions...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Others that appeared here\Nkilled two of our soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best that you don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The head is still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Others eat human brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Human brains...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There was too much that we didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We always thought the Others were merely\Na different form of disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But the daily life threatened by the Others
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,was brewing a greater conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The only that should perish...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is this crazy country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What I didn't understand the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I don't need to let fate dictate me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Because I believe that I can rewrite it♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪What's waiting for us at the world's end♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Forever eternal, keep the fire going♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Who can shake us♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Who can define us♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♪It's nothing less than our story♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Forever eternal,\Nkeep the fire going in your heart♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you did well on your first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It should take you some time\Nto finish all the reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He may sound condescending,\Nbut the original punishment was much harsher.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.29,0:23:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What was wrong with the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But for your first day,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say you did well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET GUARDIANS
